1
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:29,440
She rushed all the way
to reignite an old flame

2
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:31,720
with Na at his hotel room.

3
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,440
Don't make me ask again!

4
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,320
<i>We love each other.</i>

5
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:37,160
Pin wants a divorce,
but she's afraid you'd hurt her.

6
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,360
I'll search Pinanong's room.

7
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:39,960
No need to search.

8
00:02:40,040 --> 00:02:42,320
The medicine is in the bedroom,
dressing table drawer.

9
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,720
Mom's heart condition is acting up!

10
00:02:51,320 --> 00:02:52,920
Mr. Yai is over there. Let's go.

11
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:22,240
Let's go, Mom.

12
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:26,280
Aunt Un. Pin, let me carry her on my back.

13
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,600
Slowly, Mom.

14
00:03:33,320 --> 00:03:35,320
- Easy.
- Aunt Un.

15
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:49,600
Are you sure you want to build
a new family with me?

16
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,000
Yes.

17
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:57,160
Our little family.

18
00:04:07,480 --> 00:04:10,000
Goodbye, Pinanong.

19
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,120
Follow them. Hurry.

20
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:23,200
Catch them. Huh? Mr. Yai?

21
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:28,840
You've been shot? Hey, go catch them. Go!

22
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,200
Follow them.

23
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:36,560
That was close!

24
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:38,440
You haven't even paid me your old debt,

25
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:40,760
yet you've dragged me into trouble.

26
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:44,000
We're both his enemies,

27
00:04:44,080 --> 00:04:46,840
so he'll have to come
and settle the score with you anyway.

28
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:48,640
We're stronger together, Mr. Tong.

29
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:50,240
We'll all die together!

30
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:53,200
If you hadn't shown your face,

31
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:56,120
I might have still been able
to negotiate with him.

32
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:58,800
Enough. Enough of this.

33
00:04:58,880 --> 00:05:01,040
Hey, see our guests out.

34
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:03,720
Wait, Mr. Tong. Please calm down.

35
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:07,960
Mr. Tong, you should let us stay here.

36
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:11,000
You probably don't know

37
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:14,240
that my daughter-in-law's father is
the Permanent Secretary in the ministry.

38
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:20,240
If you welcome Na,
On will ensure her father

39
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:23,200
backs your political ambitions.

40
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:25,920
That's true.

41
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,600
The Secretary
has a lot of political power.

42
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:30,600
If he supports you,
you'll definitely win the election.

43
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:15,400
Some people act like they're trash.

44
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,800
Completely worthless.

45
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,880
I finished helping you with your work.

46
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:22,840
Can't I take a break?

47
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,320
This is my house.

48
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:30,080
Hey, hey. No need.

49
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:31,560
If you're so diligent,

50
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:33,840
go back and do it at home.

51
00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:46,080
I don't have a home.

52
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:52,680
You don't have a home?

53
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:57,360
You've been running away
from your problems since you were a kid.

54
00:06:57,440 --> 00:06:58,240
You know what?

55
00:06:58,320 --> 00:07:00,960
If a child did this, it would be pitiful.

56
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:04,000
But for a grown-ass adult like you,

57
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,160
it's just pathetic.

58
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:09,560
You created problems
and then expected others to fix them.

59
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:11,120
Not very mature, are you?

60
00:07:12,320 --> 00:07:13,480
You coward.

61
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:22,280
You two are working hard.

62
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,400
It's so beautiful.

63
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:27,440
I didn't do it. Ms. Tatsanee folded it.

64
00:07:27,520 --> 00:07:29,160
Ms. Nee was very quick to learn.

65
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:30,480
She could do it in a moment

66
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:32,960
and even came up with new designs.

67
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:37,120
She can be helpful sometimes, huh?

68
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:39,200
Mr. Pan.

69
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:42,320
I need a copy of Mr. Yai's ID card,

70
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:45,520
but he didn't sign any of them.

71
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:50,080
I'll see if there are any copies left.

72
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:52,480
When will Mr. Yai be back?

73
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:54,400
A lot of tourists are coming,

74
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:56,640
and the resort needs
a lot of improvements.

75
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:58,520
I'm afraid we will lose customers.

76
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:01,240
I really don't know.

77
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:05,320
Anyway, just let me know
if you need anything.

78
00:08:05,400 --> 00:08:07,840
I'll do anything I can during this time.

79
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:11,160
Are you planning
to take control of Paisal Farm?

80
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:15,640
Yai? Where have you been? Hey.

81
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:20,240
- Pan. Be gentle, will you?
- Dad.

82
00:08:20,320 --> 00:08:22,040
You be gentle with me, Dad.

83
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,520
Mr. Yai hasn't fully recovered yet.

84
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:24,600
You're unbelievable.

85
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:26,880
- Look at you.
- I'm okay now, Uncle.

86
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:29,160
I'm ready to do everything as promised.

87
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:31,640
I owe you and everyone an apology.

88
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:34,960
So, you mean…

89
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:38,440
I want to appear in court
to prove I'm still alive.

90
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:39,720
It's not too late, right?

91
00:08:40,919 --> 00:08:44,720
Now, that's the Mr. Yai we know.

92
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:54,920
I've made the transfer.

93
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,600
Okay, thank you.

94
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:08,560
Pin?

95
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:11,680
Pin!

96
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:22,240
Hey. You're doing bike deliveries?

97
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:25,000
Do you really make that much
selling this way?

98
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:29,840
I already have regular customers,

99
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:31,760
so it's fine.

100
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:35,760
Noi, don't tell anyone that you saw me.

101
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:40,560
I won't. If Mr. Yai knew,
he'd put you in prison.

102
00:09:43,560 --> 00:09:45,560
Pin, about the poison…

103
00:09:46,280 --> 00:09:47,920
Let's not talk about it, Noi.

104
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:54,800
So…

105
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:58,480
how's Mr. Yai doing?

106
00:09:58,560 --> 00:10:01,040
Well, Aunt Pen. Let's clink glasses.

107
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:02,200
Clink glasses?

108
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:05,000
- Come on.
- Alright, cheers.

109
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:06,680
I think he's drunk on orange juice.

110
00:10:06,760 --> 00:10:08,280
Hey, I'm not.

111
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:11,840
I'm just glad Aunt Pen came to help
with the housework.

112
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:16,640
It's just temporary, Mr. Yai.

113
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:18,400
Once you find someone new,

114
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:21,360
I'll have to hurry back
because I'm worried about things at home.

115
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:23,280
- Really?
- Hey.

116
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:27,760
When you were at the mine,
didn't you say you missed Mr. Yai and Pan?

117
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:30,800
Women really say one thing
but feel another.

118
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:31,920
What are you saying?

119
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:34,240
Here, I'm speaking my mind.

120
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:36,480
My mouth and heart are aligned too.

121
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:18,600
I told you not to do
the housework yourself.

122
00:11:18,680 --> 00:11:21,160
When your arms feel sore,
it becomes my problem.

123
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:24,240
I can just apply an ointment.

124
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:25,960
You're stubborn, huh?

125
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:27,200
Are you an old lady or something?

126
00:11:27,280 --> 00:11:29,000
You can't use ointment for everything.

127
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:30,480
Stretch your arm.

128
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:35,560
- Mr. Yai.
- Switch. The other arm's still not good.

129
00:11:35,640 --> 00:11:37,240
The other arm?

130
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:40,080
Hey.

131
00:11:40,680 --> 00:11:41,520
‪Mr. Yai.

132
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,280
Pin.

133
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:45,320
Do you need my help?

134
00:12:46,520 --> 00:12:48,600
It's okay, Mom. I'm almost done.

135
00:12:48,680 --> 00:12:49,840
You should get some rest.

136
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:52,920
No. I don't want to sleep anymore.

137
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:57,040
Every time I fall asleep,
I dream about Madam.

138
00:12:58,120 --> 00:13:01,160
I wonder how she's doing right now.

139
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:29,640
Stealing my stuff?

140
00:13:32,240 --> 00:13:33,240
I'm not.

141
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,760
Where are you going?

142
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:37,320
Are you trying to run away?

143
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:42,920
You bitch.

144
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:44,720
How ungrateful and unappreciative.

145
00:13:44,800 --> 00:13:47,520
You let us stay because
you wanted something in return too.

146
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:49,320
What gratitude are you talking about?

147
00:13:51,160 --> 00:13:52,800
You're the mouthy one, huh? Come here.

148
00:13:54,800 --> 00:13:56,960
- Let go, you old fart!
- Wanna do something in return?

149
00:13:57,040 --> 00:13:59,240
- Let go!
- Wanna have an old husband?

150
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:01,360
Come here. Come with me.

151
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:04,320
Stop it, Mr. Tong.

152
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:06,760
What are you going to do to my niece?

153
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:09,480
She came into my room and stole something.

154
00:14:09,560 --> 00:14:10,960
You ungrateful bunch.

155
00:14:12,400 --> 00:14:13,680
Is that true?

156
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:17,200
He was the one forcing himself on me.

157
00:14:23,000 --> 00:14:26,320
Go outside. Go.

158
00:14:30,360 --> 00:14:33,400
Mr. Tong, my niece is depressed.

159
00:14:33,480 --> 00:14:34,960
Please don't hold it against her.

160
00:14:35,560 --> 00:14:37,440
I can't trust any of you.

161
00:14:37,520 --> 00:14:39,720
Get out of my house. Go.

162
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:43,480
Come on.

163
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:47,280
Please calm down first. Alright?

164
00:14:47,880 --> 00:14:49,840
Let's talk about it.

165
00:15:16,240 --> 00:15:17,200
Hey.

166
00:15:20,080 --> 00:15:22,640
I'm Madam's secretary. Don't you remember?

167
00:15:22,720 --> 00:15:24,800
The boss ordered that no one be let in.

168
00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:29,760
Where are you going?

169
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:35,240
There, there.

170
00:15:36,760 --> 00:15:37,640
- Hey!
- Hey.

171
00:15:40,920 --> 00:15:41,720
Come here.

172
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:47,080
Krong. What is this? What are you doing?

173
00:15:47,880 --> 00:15:49,000
You're asking a stupid question.

174
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:51,720
It's obvious. Do I need to explain?

175
00:15:54,640 --> 00:15:56,320
You want to know, huh?

176
00:15:56,400 --> 00:15:59,280
You want to know?

177
00:16:06,040 --> 00:16:08,400
What should we do with your main man?

178
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:12,240
It's up to you. I don't care.

179
00:16:13,880 --> 00:16:17,760
Hey. Drag him away
and deal with him far from my sight.

180
00:16:18,400 --> 00:16:19,680
- Yes, Boss.
- Yes, Boss.

181
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:21,880
Krong.

182
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:25,040
You can't do this to me.

183
00:16:26,040 --> 00:16:29,640
I've always been loyal to you,
risked my life for you.

184
00:16:30,680 --> 00:16:32,920
Krong. Krong.

185
00:16:34,160 --> 00:16:35,400
- Let go of me.
- Come here.

186
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:38,440
- Let go. I said let go.
- Come.

187
00:16:38,520 --> 00:16:39,520
Let me go.

188
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:41,000
- Come here.
- Let go.

189
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:44,520
Let go! Krong!

190
00:17:13,079 --> 00:17:14,040
- Come here!
- Jom. Stop.

191
00:17:15,839 --> 00:17:17,960
Who are you? Let him go.

192
00:17:18,040 --> 00:17:19,280
No. Don't do this.

193
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:25,599
- Jom.
- Mom.

194
00:17:28,760 --> 00:17:30,120
- Jom.
- Mom!

195
00:17:30,760 --> 00:17:32,760
Mom. Mom.

196
00:17:32,840 --> 00:17:34,960
I'll give you one more day,

197
00:17:35,040 --> 00:17:37,000
or I'll kill your whole family.

198
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:39,960
Let's go!

199
00:17:40,040 --> 00:17:42,200
Mom. Mom.

200
00:17:43,320 --> 00:17:45,240
Mom. Mom.

201
00:17:52,120 --> 00:17:55,360
We found a new blockage
in the coronary artery

202
00:17:55,440 --> 00:17:58,560
but not to the extent that
another angioplasty would be necessary.

203
00:18:00,920 --> 00:18:03,160
Weren't you supposed
to take care of Pin and Aunt Un?

204
00:18:03,240 --> 00:18:05,160
You're just causing Pin more trouble.

205
00:18:06,640 --> 00:18:08,320
I didn't want Pin to struggle,

206
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:10,480
so I borrowed from the loan shark
and bought a bike for Pin.

207
00:18:10,560 --> 00:18:11,800
Was I that wrong?

208
00:18:17,240 --> 00:18:19,480
Pin. How is Aunt Un?

209
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:22,240
Another stenosis, Jin.

210
00:18:22,840 --> 00:18:24,160
I'm sorry, Pin.

211
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:28,840
Sell this ring and use the money
to pay off that debt, Jom.

212
00:18:29,480 --> 00:18:31,160
But this is your wedding ring.

213
00:18:32,840 --> 00:18:35,240
Okay, I'll sell it for you.

214
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:39,360
It was just a minor scald.

215
00:18:39,440 --> 00:18:41,400
You didn't need to drive me.

216
00:18:41,480 --> 00:18:43,240
I could have even driven here myself.

217
00:18:43,320 --> 00:18:45,360
When I was injured
by shrapnel from the mine,

218
00:18:45,440 --> 00:18:47,280
you stayed by my side every night.

219
00:18:47,360 --> 00:18:49,200
You were basically living in the hospital.

220
00:18:49,280 --> 00:18:51,160
This time, I had to repay you.

221
00:18:53,480 --> 00:18:55,360
But I think…

222
00:18:56,440 --> 00:18:59,800
maybe you're just trying
to keep yourself busy.

223
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:01,360
Right?

224
00:19:04,840 --> 00:19:06,400
Over here, please.

225
00:19:06,480 --> 00:19:07,360
Yes.

226
00:19:21,480 --> 00:19:23,080
- Oh, sorry.
- Sorry.

227
00:19:41,840 --> 00:19:43,200
I'm sorry, dear.

228
00:19:43,280 --> 00:19:45,320
The space is a bit cramped.

229
00:19:45,400 --> 00:19:46,560
Yes. It's okay.

230
00:19:55,760 --> 00:19:57,720
Excuse me. Do you remember me?

231
00:20:06,600 --> 00:20:07,840
Pin.

232
00:20:08,840 --> 00:20:10,440
Why did you have to move me here?

233
00:20:10,520 --> 00:20:12,280
Do you have that much money to spare?

234
00:20:12,360 --> 00:20:13,760
I'm fine now.

235
00:20:13,840 --> 00:20:15,760
Let's go home.

236
00:20:16,560 --> 00:20:18,240
- Mom.
- Let's go.

237
00:20:18,320 --> 00:20:19,600
Don't worry, Un.

238
00:20:20,200 --> 00:20:22,920
Someone has offered to take care of you.

239
00:20:24,040 --> 00:20:25,600
Mom, lie down.

240
00:20:28,160 --> 00:20:29,400
Who was it, Aunt Da?

241
00:20:29,480 --> 00:20:32,920
Our hospital has a program
to help patients in need.

242
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:35,680
The benefactors will donate
through that program.

243
00:20:36,880 --> 00:20:38,720
May I know their name?

244
00:20:38,800 --> 00:20:40,040
I'd like to thank them.

245
00:20:40,120 --> 00:20:41,520
I'm afraid I can't tell you, Pin.

246
00:20:41,600 --> 00:20:43,720
They wish to remain anonymous.

247
00:20:45,800 --> 00:20:47,520
They're so kind-hearted.

248
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:53,720
I wish you all the best.

249
00:20:56,280 --> 00:20:57,640
Thank you very much.

250
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:01,480
Here's my phone number.

251
00:21:01,560 --> 00:21:05,040
If there's anything urgent
regarding Aunt Un, please let me know.

252
00:21:05,120 --> 00:21:08,480
If you hadn't told me
you were Mr. Paisal's son,

253
00:21:08,560 --> 00:21:10,520
I definitely wouldn't have remembered you.

254
00:21:12,880 --> 00:21:14,280
Are you sure

255
00:21:14,360 --> 00:21:17,240
my father wasn't poisoned?

256
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:19,040
He wasn't.

257
00:21:19,600 --> 00:21:22,680
The doctor diagnosed it
as muscle weakness.

258
00:21:22,760 --> 00:21:24,680
That's why he couldn't communicate.

259
00:21:25,600 --> 00:21:27,320
Madam Krongsuk was well aware of this,

260
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:29,360
so she chose
to take him back for home care.

261
00:21:29,440 --> 00:21:34,040
And Pin was coming to pick up the meds
and update the doctor about the symptoms,

262
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:38,840
since she was his caregiver at that time.

263
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:42,160
- Please excuse me.
- Yes.

264
00:21:59,520 --> 00:22:01,800
Pan. You couldn't find it, right?

265
00:22:29,920 --> 00:22:32,720
You think making a small merit
will atone for your sin?

266
00:22:56,600 --> 00:23:00,160
She's acting just as I did
when I was pregnant. No doubt about it.

267
00:23:00,240 --> 00:23:02,640
- She's definitely pregnant.
- I think she is.

268
00:23:15,960 --> 00:23:17,000
Mr. Yai?

269
00:23:18,840 --> 00:23:20,520
What are you doing here?

270
00:23:22,880 --> 00:23:23,840
Why did you come to the hospital?

271
00:23:23,920 --> 00:23:24,920
What's wrong?

272
00:23:26,280 --> 00:23:28,920
You let me and Mom go, didn't you?

273
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:30,440
So why do you keep following me?

274
00:23:31,040 --> 00:23:32,360
I've changed my mind.

275
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:34,480
I'm going to drag you and your mom
to face the consequences.

276
00:23:34,560 --> 00:23:35,560
Come here.

277
00:23:37,080 --> 00:23:39,680
Mr. Yai. Mr. Yai, please.

278
00:23:40,320 --> 00:23:42,560
Can you let Mom recover first?

279
00:23:42,640 --> 00:23:44,720
Then I'll turn myself in to the police.

280
00:23:45,760 --> 00:23:47,160
You think I'd still believe you?

281
00:23:47,240 --> 00:23:49,720
If you don't want me to turn your mom in,

282
00:23:49,800 --> 00:23:51,200
then tell me the whole truth.

283
00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:20,640
It was just a moment of selfishness.

284
00:24:23,320 --> 00:24:25,200
I let you down.

285
00:24:27,520 --> 00:24:30,400
I don't know
how to make up for this mistake,

286
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:33,760
other than paying for it
with my worthless life.

287
00:24:34,920 --> 00:24:37,760
Pin, don't threaten me.
Back away from there.

288
00:24:44,120 --> 00:24:46,760
Can I trade my life for my mom's?

289
00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:51,320
No, Pin. A quick death would be too easy.

290
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:52,520
I'll torture you myself.

291
00:24:52,600 --> 00:24:53,520
Give me your hands.

292
00:24:57,960 --> 00:24:59,000
Now.

293
00:25:00,480 --> 00:25:01,880
I'm sorry.

294
00:25:04,960 --> 00:25:07,440
I'm sorry for upsetting you.

295
00:25:14,440 --> 00:25:16,000
Pin! Pin.

296
00:25:17,640 --> 00:25:19,400
Pin. Pin.

297
00:25:20,680 --> 00:25:23,680
Pin? What were you going to do to her?

298
00:25:27,560 --> 00:25:29,160
Let go of her right now.

299
00:25:30,720 --> 00:25:31,560
Pin.

300
00:25:39,000 --> 00:25:40,280
I'm begging you.

301
00:25:41,320 --> 00:25:42,680
Let Pin go.

302
00:25:43,560 --> 00:25:45,800
This is enough punishment for her.

303
00:25:47,360 --> 00:25:49,360
Is Pin suffering from any serious illness?

304
00:25:50,000 --> 00:25:51,160
I don't know.

305
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:55,440
All I know is that every day, she drives
her bike in the hot sun to deliver food.

306
00:25:55,520 --> 00:25:58,600
She doesn't get to eat or sleep much.

307
00:25:58,680 --> 00:26:01,240
And she also has
to take care of her sick mother.

308
00:26:02,000 --> 00:26:03,640
It's no wonder she collapsed.

309
00:26:05,240 --> 00:26:06,920
- Yai.
- Hey. Jom.

310
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:08,240
What did you do to Pin again?

311
00:26:08,320 --> 00:26:09,680
I was clearing things up with my wife.

312
00:26:09,760 --> 00:26:11,080
Outsiders shouldn't butt in.

313
00:26:11,680 --> 00:26:13,120
Hey, Jom, don't.

314
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:15,840
This is a hospital. Just calm down.

315
00:26:15,920 --> 00:26:17,800
- Jom.
- Jom?

316
00:26:18,640 --> 00:26:19,680
Pin.

317
00:26:19,760 --> 00:26:21,960
Pin. What did the doctor say?

318
00:26:26,480 --> 00:26:28,280
- Hey. Wait, wait.
- Pin?

319
00:26:29,120 --> 00:26:30,280
In here.

320
00:26:39,000 --> 00:26:40,640
So what exactly is your condition?

321
00:26:44,280 --> 00:26:45,600
Could you be pregnant?

322
00:26:49,880 --> 00:26:50,960
If you're pregnant

323
00:26:51,040 --> 00:26:54,200
and the baby is mine,
I have a right to know.

324
00:26:55,280 --> 00:26:57,680
But if you plan
to keep the baby to yourself,

325
00:26:57,760 --> 00:27:00,320
I'll sue you for full custody.

326
00:27:03,600 --> 00:27:05,400
- I'm not--
- She's two months pregnant.

327
00:27:12,360 --> 00:27:15,960
Pin. Why didn't you tell me
you're carrying my baby?

328
00:27:17,920 --> 00:27:19,000
Huh?

329
00:27:22,880 --> 00:27:26,600
The baby in Pin's womb is mine.

330
00:27:35,360 --> 00:27:36,960
You're lying.

331
00:27:37,560 --> 00:27:38,520
Jom.

332
00:27:40,280 --> 00:27:43,880
You told me yourself that you didn't want
Mr. Yai to know you're pregnant

333
00:27:44,480 --> 00:27:46,120
because you were afraid
Mr. Yai would hurt us.

334
00:27:46,200 --> 00:27:47,440
But now, we're not afraid.

335
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:50,240
You can go see our house if you want.

336
00:27:50,320 --> 00:27:51,600
I'll take you there myself.

337
00:28:03,840 --> 00:28:04,840
Pin.

338
00:28:06,560 --> 00:28:08,840
Didn't you want him
to stop messing with you?

339
00:28:09,600 --> 00:28:10,760
I already helped you.

340
00:28:11,360 --> 00:28:14,600
Jom, who are you
to meddle in other people's lives?

341
00:28:14,680 --> 00:28:17,400
And are you really pregnant or not?

342
00:28:34,360 --> 00:28:37,880
Mr. Yai, do you really believe

343
00:28:38,480 --> 00:28:40,400
that Pin is pregnant with Jom's child?

344
00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:47,080
I wanted to hear her deny everything,
the pregnancy, the drugging.

345
00:28:47,160 --> 00:28:49,520
But Noi told me

346
00:28:49,600 --> 00:28:51,080
that she saw Pin

347
00:28:51,160 --> 00:28:54,200
throw away the food her mom made for you

348
00:28:54,280 --> 00:28:55,480
so many times.

349
00:28:56,200 --> 00:28:58,720
But that doesn't prove anything. It's…

350
00:28:58,800 --> 00:29:00,400
Mr. Yai.

351
00:29:01,360 --> 00:29:04,520
You must know Pin better than anyone.

352
00:29:16,800 --> 00:29:17,920
<i>Good news.</i>

353
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:22,000
<i>The court has rescinded the order</i>
<i>declaring you a missing person.</i>

354
00:29:22,080 --> 00:29:24,600
<i>So, get ready to inherit the will.</i>

355
00:29:29,720 --> 00:29:30,720
But the problem is,

356
00:29:30,800 --> 00:29:35,920
Krongsuk was legally married to your dad
and has the right to half of the fortune.

357
00:29:36,840 --> 00:29:37,840
That's weird.

358
00:29:38,720 --> 00:29:41,120
Why didn't she claim that right
in court from the start?

359
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:44,960
I think she's tied to your dad's murder,
just as we suspected.

360
00:29:45,040 --> 00:29:47,920
Think about it. She dared to poison you.

361
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:49,720
Couldn't Mr. Paisal have easily suffered
the same fate?

362
00:29:49,800 --> 00:29:51,520
But we don't have any evidence.

363
00:29:51,600 --> 00:29:53,000
How am I supposed to fight it?

364
00:29:53,080 --> 00:29:55,160
Just report her to the police.

365
00:29:55,720 --> 00:29:59,080
Once it becomes a legal case, people will
help us investigate and find evidence.

366
00:29:59,160 --> 00:30:02,680
<i>And if Krongsuk is really guilty,</i>
<i>she won't get the inheritance.</i>

367
00:30:02,760 --> 00:30:04,880
It's now up to you if you dare to do it,

368
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:08,320
because Aunt Un would also be implicated.

369
00:30:12,040 --> 00:30:14,960
Whatever. I can wait.

370
00:30:15,040 --> 00:30:17,240
But I don't know
if Dad will be as patient.

371
00:30:19,920 --> 00:30:22,720
- Is this because of Pinanong, Mr. Yai?
- Dad.

372
00:30:22,800 --> 00:30:24,000
Uncle Pload?

373
00:30:24,080 --> 00:30:28,880
If won't take action,
I'll have to teach them a lesson myself.

374
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:31,880
I'll make them both regret
what they've done.

375
00:30:31,960 --> 00:30:33,040
Uncle Pload, please wait.

376
00:30:33,120 --> 00:30:36,480
I was already planning
to handle this myself.

377
00:30:36,560 --> 00:30:39,360
I just need some time to think it through.

378
00:30:40,520 --> 00:30:42,560
I won't go easy on them this time.

379
00:30:45,280 --> 00:30:46,480
Dad, calm down.

380
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:55,480
On. You're finally here.

381
00:30:55,560 --> 00:30:56,560
Hello.

382
00:30:56,640 --> 00:31:00,240
Ms. Onsa-ang, I'm Tong,
the owner of this house.

383
00:31:01,120 --> 00:31:05,520
It's a great honor to welcome the
Permanent Secretary's beautiful daughter.

384
00:31:11,800 --> 00:31:14,520
Why do you have to tolerate
living with this thug?

385
00:31:15,800 --> 00:31:19,280
Because Mr. Tong will help Na
take back the inheritance from Yai.

386
00:31:19,360 --> 00:31:22,840
And you have to use
your father's influence

387
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:25,400
to get him
into a political party as he wants.

388
00:31:26,960 --> 00:31:27,840
But now, the Secretary…

389
00:31:30,400 --> 00:31:33,120
This is just a small matter for my father.

390
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:35,920
So, is everything

391
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:39,520
really cleared up at your house?

392
00:31:41,280 --> 00:31:45,600
It was just a story
fabricated to slander my father.

393
00:31:45,680 --> 00:31:50,800
As for his debt, selling land for three
or four hundred million would settle it.

394
00:31:50,880 --> 00:31:51,840
Right, Jan?

395
00:31:53,480 --> 00:31:56,360
Yes. There won't be any more problems.

396
00:31:57,440 --> 00:31:58,920
If that's the case, that's good.

397
00:32:00,760 --> 00:32:01,680
Na?

398
00:32:03,440 --> 00:32:04,760
I'm sorry.

399
00:32:18,480 --> 00:32:22,320
What's wrong? Why won't you talk to me?

400
00:32:22,400 --> 00:32:25,440
Auntie said you were the one
who asked her to bring me back.

401
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:28,200
I need to go out for a bit.

402
00:32:28,280 --> 00:32:30,320
Where are you going? I'm coming with you.

403
00:32:30,920 --> 00:32:31,760
You don't need to.

404
00:32:32,280 --> 00:32:34,560
You've just arrived. Get some rest.

405
00:32:36,280 --> 00:32:37,240
Na.

406
00:32:40,080 --> 00:32:43,600
I agreed to come here because I love you.

407
00:32:44,280 --> 00:32:45,680
I promise

408
00:32:45,760 --> 00:32:49,200
that I'll help you get everything back,

409
00:32:50,760 --> 00:32:53,480
so we can start a new life abroad.

410
00:32:54,600 --> 00:32:56,640
Once you've actually
cleared everything up,

411
00:32:58,280 --> 00:32:59,400
then we'll talk.

412
00:33:03,840 --> 00:33:05,960
Na. Na.

413
00:33:24,280 --> 00:33:25,200
Pin.

414
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:29,160
Give it back.

415
00:33:30,160 --> 00:33:31,760
I need to go somewhere.

416
00:33:33,240 --> 00:33:34,440
Are you going to see this bitch?

417
00:33:34,520 --> 00:33:36,480
You're pretending to be upset with me

418
00:33:36,560 --> 00:33:38,880
just to go and be with this lowly girl.

419
00:33:41,200 --> 00:33:44,760
On the contrary, she's too high up.

420
00:33:45,760 --> 00:33:47,320
She's too high for me to reach.

421
00:33:49,120 --> 00:33:53,080
It was me who was too blind
to see only you.

422
00:33:56,800 --> 00:33:59,960
How dare you insult me like that!

423
00:34:05,040 --> 00:34:05,880
Give it back.

424
00:34:07,120 --> 00:34:08,600
- I won't give it. Na.
- On.

425
00:34:08,679 --> 00:34:10,600
- I won't let you go to her.
- Give it back.

426
00:34:10,679 --> 00:34:11,679
I won't.

427
00:34:11,760 --> 00:34:12,719
‪Give it back!

428
00:34:14,400 --> 00:34:16,480
Miss On. Miss On.

429
00:34:16,560 --> 00:34:18,840
Mr. Na, you've gone too far.

430
00:34:18,920 --> 00:34:22,120
Miss On lowered herself by being here
because she loves you.

431
00:34:27,239 --> 00:34:29,840
I know, and I'm very grateful.

432
00:34:31,159 --> 00:34:33,199
So, prove your love

433
00:34:33,920 --> 00:34:36,360
by fulfilling your promise to Mr. Tong.

434
00:34:37,520 --> 00:34:38,719
Only then will I believe

435
00:34:39,480 --> 00:34:41,199
how much you love me…

436
00:34:43,040 --> 00:34:44,520
that you really love me.

437
00:34:51,560 --> 00:34:53,760
How did Mr. Na become like this?

438
00:34:56,639 --> 00:34:59,000
Pin. Pinanong.

439
00:35:05,920 --> 00:35:07,680
It's because of Pinanong!

440
00:35:07,760 --> 00:35:11,680
Pinanong made Na upset with me.

441
00:35:12,400 --> 00:35:14,400
There's no way I'll lose to her.

442
00:35:49,080 --> 00:35:52,400
Stop. If you won't, let's see
what the Internet has to say.

443
00:36:30,000 --> 00:36:31,120
Thank you.

444
00:36:33,560 --> 00:36:35,000
I need to talk to you.

445
00:36:36,800 --> 00:36:37,960
If you want to ask about that--

446
00:36:38,040 --> 00:36:39,920
Let's get the divorce.

447
00:36:44,720 --> 00:36:48,200
Even if you're not pregnant,
I was divorcing you anyway.

448
00:36:48,960 --> 00:36:50,760
I won't waste my time on someone like you.

449
00:36:59,080 --> 00:37:00,720
As you wish.

450
00:37:07,920 --> 00:37:09,800
Then you can schedule it.

451
00:37:09,880 --> 00:37:11,360
The sooner, the better.

452
00:37:11,440 --> 00:37:14,120
So I'll be able to settle
the score quickly.

453
00:37:15,440 --> 00:37:16,760
Since we've cut ties,

454
00:37:16,840 --> 00:37:19,200
there's no need for pleasantries
or saving face anymore,

455
00:37:19,280 --> 00:37:21,240
whether it's your mom or Jom.

456
00:37:25,240 --> 00:37:26,480
What are you going to do?

457
00:37:33,320 --> 00:37:35,200
You'll see that I'm worse than you think.

458
00:38:21,760 --> 00:38:23,480
Don't you have any self-control?

459
00:38:23,560 --> 00:38:25,240
You can't even think straight.

460
00:38:27,640 --> 00:38:29,200
She already has a child with Jom.

461
00:38:29,280 --> 00:38:31,040
Your marriage is unsalvageable.

462
00:38:31,120 --> 00:38:34,600
If she really wants
to divorce me, I'll grant it.

463
00:38:35,600 --> 00:38:37,680
Then I'll drag Aunt Un
to the police station,

464
00:38:37,760 --> 00:38:39,000
so she can hate me.

465
00:38:39,720 --> 00:38:41,040
I'll end things with her for good.

466
00:38:41,120 --> 00:38:42,400
Satisfied now?

467
00:38:43,920 --> 00:38:47,480
Way to go. That's how Mr. Yai should be.

468
00:39:04,600 --> 00:39:06,680
Mr. Tong is asleep. What do you want?

469
00:39:07,280 --> 00:39:09,160
I'm here to report on Yai and Pin.

470
00:39:09,240 --> 00:39:10,440
What about them?

471
00:39:11,040 --> 00:39:14,840
I saw the two of them holding hands
on the street in front of the hospital.

472
00:39:14,920 --> 00:39:16,640
I don't see any signs of them fighting.

473
00:39:16,720 --> 00:39:18,680
So, what were they doing
near that hospital?

474
00:39:18,760 --> 00:39:20,520
I asked around.

475
00:39:20,600 --> 00:39:22,920
Pinanong took her mom
to that hospital for treatment.

476
00:39:34,840 --> 00:39:36,360
What are you doing here?

477
00:39:37,920 --> 00:39:40,400
If you want to make us pay,
just take me alone.

478
00:39:42,120 --> 00:39:43,440
I'm her family.

479
00:39:43,520 --> 00:39:45,120
Please let me bring her inside.

480
00:39:45,720 --> 00:39:46,720
Yes.

481
00:39:47,680 --> 00:39:50,200
Wait. Nurse.

482
00:39:50,280 --> 00:39:51,960
I hired a private nurse myself.

483
00:39:53,560 --> 00:39:54,760
Of course, she'd listen to me.

484
00:40:12,960 --> 00:40:15,240
Hey, what are you going to do?

485
00:40:22,120 --> 00:40:23,480
Let's go to the police.

486
00:40:25,040 --> 00:40:27,160
You must tell the police the truth

487
00:40:27,240 --> 00:40:30,960
that Madam ordered you to drug me,
so Pin wouldn't be in trouble.

488
00:40:31,640 --> 00:40:33,960
No. Madam didn't do it.
She wasn't involved.

489
00:40:34,040 --> 00:40:35,360
It was me. I acted alone.

490
00:40:35,440 --> 00:40:38,280
I don't understand
why you're so willing to help that witch.

491
00:40:38,360 --> 00:40:41,520
It's because you never appreciate
the kindness of your parents,

492
00:40:41,600 --> 00:40:43,640
so you'd never understand
how I feel, right?

493
00:40:43,720 --> 00:40:44,800
She killed Pha, Aunt Un.

494
00:40:46,600 --> 00:40:49,080
And she probably poisoned
and killed my father too,

495
00:40:49,160 --> 00:40:51,240
the same way she ordered you to poison me.

496
00:40:56,440 --> 00:40:58,400
It was you who killed Pha.

497
00:40:58,960 --> 00:41:00,280
See for yourself, Aunt Un.

498
00:41:06,440 --> 00:41:08,160
Pha died after being hit by a car.

499
00:41:08,240 --> 00:41:10,800
Someone deliberately
and brutally ran him over

500
00:41:10,880 --> 00:41:12,880
after I left Paisal Farm.

501
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:19,320
You should know your madam
better than anyone.

502
00:41:19,400 --> 00:41:22,600
You should know what kind of things
that cruel woman is capable of.

503
00:41:23,200 --> 00:41:26,960
If she could poison me,
she could poison my father too.

504
00:41:30,560 --> 00:41:34,080
Your blind love and gratitude

505
00:41:35,240 --> 00:41:37,160
are destroying everyone's lives,

506
00:41:37,680 --> 00:41:39,440
including your own daughter's.

507
00:41:45,880 --> 00:41:47,200
You might already know

508
00:41:47,720 --> 00:41:49,720
if I file a police report

509
00:41:49,800 --> 00:41:53,280
who will sacrifice herself to help you.

510
00:41:59,880 --> 00:42:02,880
But… But Pin used to be your wife.

511
00:42:02,960 --> 00:42:04,720
That's why I came to warn you.

512
00:42:06,640 --> 00:42:09,280
I'm giving you just one night to decide.

513
00:42:10,720 --> 00:42:12,680
I'll come back tomorrow
to hear your answer.

514
00:42:50,680 --> 00:42:53,920
Mr. Tong, I need your help.

515
00:43:06,000 --> 00:43:08,360
Aunt Da, where did Mom go?

516
00:43:08,440 --> 00:43:13,360
Well, your husband informed the hospital
that he would like to take Un home.

517
00:43:14,720 --> 00:43:18,080
And all expenses have been settled
with the finance department.

518
00:43:18,160 --> 00:43:19,480
My husband?

519
00:43:19,560 --> 00:43:21,000
Mr. Yai.

520
00:43:21,560 --> 00:43:24,400
Didn't he tell you he's the one
who was covering all the medical bills

521
00:43:24,480 --> 00:43:26,720
and the room expenses?

522
00:43:30,440 --> 00:43:31,320
That bastard.

523
00:43:32,120 --> 00:43:33,720
He's trying to get back at Aunt Un.

524
00:43:50,680 --> 00:43:52,560
I'll go check out Aunt Un's old house.

525
00:43:53,240 --> 00:43:54,440
Be careful, Jom.

526
00:43:54,520 --> 00:43:56,080
Don't get into
any more fights with anyone.

527
00:43:56,160 --> 00:43:57,960
Just ask the workers or Piak.

528
00:43:58,760 --> 00:43:59,760
Alright.

529
00:44:20,760 --> 00:44:22,040
Let go of me!

530
00:44:24,560 --> 00:44:25,640
Pin.

531
00:44:34,080 --> 00:44:37,040
You think I'm some woman off the streets
that you can do whatever you want with?

532
00:44:38,000 --> 00:44:39,920
Keep it down. You were too loud.

533
00:44:40,000 --> 00:44:41,600
You're done for if Uncle Pload hears you.

534
00:44:41,680 --> 00:44:43,280
He isn't as kind as I am.

535
00:44:43,360 --> 00:44:44,960
Don't threaten me.

536
00:44:45,040 --> 00:44:46,640
I'm not afraid of anything anymore.

537
00:44:46,720 --> 00:44:48,360
Give me back my mom.

538
00:44:48,440 --> 00:44:51,000
Aunt Un? Where did she disappear to?

539
00:44:51,080 --> 00:44:53,960
You told me yourself
that you would get back at my mom.

540
00:44:54,040 --> 00:44:57,520
And the hospital confirmed that you
were the one who asked to take Mom out.

541
00:44:58,320 --> 00:45:01,880
So did you pay for everything
because you wanted revenge?

542
00:45:01,960 --> 00:45:03,120
Mr. Yai, I'm begging you.

543
00:45:03,200 --> 00:45:04,480
Mom's very unwell.

544
00:45:04,560 --> 00:45:06,080
Give me back my mom.

545
00:45:06,160 --> 00:45:07,680
You can take my life instead.

546
00:45:07,760 --> 00:45:11,360
Pin. I did go to see Aunt Un,
but I didn't take her out.

547
00:45:11,440 --> 00:45:12,280
I just asked her to confess.

548
00:45:12,360 --> 00:45:14,000
She might have been scared and ran away.

549
00:45:17,360 --> 00:45:18,480
Pin.

550
00:45:19,400 --> 00:45:22,920
Mr. Paisal fell ill and died

551
00:45:23,000 --> 00:45:25,880
because you poisoned him?

552
00:45:25,960 --> 00:45:27,320
I'm really sorry, Un.

553
00:45:31,720 --> 00:45:34,880
I'll kill Yai
and wash Aunt Un's feet with his blood.

554
00:46:23,440 --> 00:46:25,680
Subtitle translation by: Anan Pratchayakul
